00:40:18,241 --> 00:40:20,156
- How are we gonna pay it?

805
00:40:20,200 --> 00:40:21,462
And now you're saying
this case could drag on

806
00:40:21,506 --> 00:40:23,769
for another year?

807
00:40:23,812 --> 00:40:25,901
You've got to give it up.

808
00:40:28,121 --> 00:40:29,470
- You know, Paul.

809
00:40:29,514 --> 00:40:31,777
I don't know if you
can ever understand.

810
00:40:31,820 --> 00:40:34,040
- I feel like you care
more about Lindsey Scott

