- The transfer order's legit.

826
00:41:31,706 --> 00:41:33,012
There's nothing we
can do about it.

827
00:41:33,055 --> 00:41:34,274
- Funny they should do
it right when you file

828
00:41:34,317 --> 00:41:35,405
for a new trial and
a Dubay hearing.

829
00:41:35,449 --> 00:41:36,232
- I know.

830
00:41:38,539 --> 00:41:42,108
You need to make time
work for you in there.

831
00:41:43,805 --> 00:41:44,589
Use it.

832
00:41:46,416 --> 00:41:48,375
You need to get yourself
in the right mindset

833
00:41:48,418 --> 00:41:50,029
