00:42:28,850 --> 00:42:31,766
[march-like music]

841
00:42:42,734 --> 00:42:44,474
- [Crowd] Free Lindsey Scott.

842
00:42:44,518 --> 00:42:46,041
Free Lindsey Scott.

843
00:42:46,085 --> 00:42:47,565
- [Reporter] Mrs. Jackson,
you obviously believe

844
00:42:47,608 --> 00:42:49,567
Lindsey Scott is
