You're old enough now to
realize that the world can be

872
00:44:09,037 --> 00:44:11,213
a very hard and unfair place.

873
00:44:11,257 --> 00:44:13,563
So, you've got to
fight for yourself.

874
00:44:13,607 --> 00:44:16,262
Ain't nobody gonna
do that for you.

875
00:44:16,305 --> 00:44:18,438
If we don't take
care of things today,

876
00:44:18,481 --> 00:44:21,789
the future's just
gonna be worse, baby.

877
00:44:29,405 --> 00:44:30,189
Dena?

878
00:44:33,322 --> 00:44:35,411
[dog barking]

879
00:44:35,455 --> 00:44:37,196
- I'm telling you,
it's not too far

880
00:44:37,239 --> 00:44:38,588
and it's right on the lake,

881
00:44:38,632 --> 00:44:40,416
