get some peace and quiet.

882
00:44:40,460 --> 00:44:41,591
- Here, baby.

883
00:44:41,635 --> 00:44:42,810
- Mama, phone.

884
00:44:44,594 --> 00:44:45,944
- Whoa.

885
00:44:45,987 --> 00:44:49,556
No matter who, or what,
that is, we're still going.

886
00:44:50,470 --> 00:44:51,993
Repeat after me.

887
00:44:52,037 --> 00:44:55,780
No matter who, or what,
that is, we are still going.

888
00:44:58,173 --> 00:44:59,479
- [Lori] Hello?

