00:45:00,741 --> 00:45:01,481
Yes, this is Lori Jackson.

890
00:45:01,524 --> 00:45:02,569
- Thanks.

891
00:45:05,746 --> 00:45:07,269
- 60 Minutes called.

892
00:45:07,313 --> 00:45:09,576
