about the Lindsey Scott case.

893
00:45:09,619 --> 00:45:10,403
- Oh, my god!

894
00:45:10,446 --> 00:45:11,491
I've gotta tell Kelly!

895
00:45:11,534 --> 00:45:13,449
- How did that happen?

896
00:45:13,493 --> 00:45:15,451
- [Lori] Well, I
