897
00:45:15,495 --> 00:45:16,975
- That's great, that's great.

898
00:45:17,018 --> 00:45:19,586
When are they coming?

899
00:45:19,629 --> 00:45:20,500
- Tomorrow.

900
00:45:22,545 --> 00:45:25,374
[subdued music]

901
00:45:31,467 --> 00:45:33,731
- I said I was going fishing.

902
00:45:35,776 --> 00:45:37,560
So, I'm going fishing.

903
00:45:49,703 --> 00:45:50,922
- [Man] All right, everybody.

904
00:45:50,965 --> 00:45:54,577
We're ready to start
taping in 10 minutes.

905
00:45:54,621 --> 00:45:55,753
- [Crewman] Set it right here?

906
00:45:55,796 --> 00:45:58,668
- [Man] Yeah, that's good.

907
00:45:58,712 --> 00:46:00,409
Kick off that lamp.

908
00:46:01,584 --> 00:46:03,108
Let's do a sound check
on her, all right?

909
00:46:03,151 --> 00:46:05,458
- [Crewman] All right.

910
00:46:05,501 --> 00:46:07,721
- [Man] That's good.

911
00:46:07,765 --> 00:46:09,549
Oh, that's too bright.

912
00:46:11,290 --> 00:46:12,117
- Oh, my god.

913
00:46:12,160 --> 00:46:12,900
Come on, honey.

914
00:46:12,944 --> 00:46:14,554
Hurry, hurry.

915
00:46:14,597 --> 00:46:15,816
You don't know when
you're coming on.

916
00:46:15,860 --> 00:46:16,730
You could be right at the top.

917
00:46:16,774 --> 00:46:18,601
So, we don't want to miss it.

918
00:46:18,645 --> 00:46:19,864
- Can I get anybody
something else to drink?

919
00:46:19,907 --> 00:46:20,690
- No, no, no.

920
00:46:20,734 --> 00:46:21,474
Go sit down.

921
00:46:21,517 --> 00:46:22,388
Watch your show.

922
00:46:22,431 --> 00:46:23,302
Now, this is your moment.

923
00:46:23,345 --> 00:46:24,259
- Come sit down.

924
00:46:24,303 --> 00:46:25,391
- I got my drink.

925
00:46:25,434 --> 00:46:26,218
I'm fine.

926
00:46:27,436 --> 00:46:30,613
- I hope I have
enough makeup on.

927
00:46:30,657 --> 00:46:31,397
- Am I late?

928
00:46:31,440 --> 00:46:32,441
- No.

929
00:46:32,485 --> 00:46:34,008
It's just now starting.

930
00:46:34,052 --> 00:46:36,402
- [Man On TV] Corporal Lindsey
Scott, Marine Corps prisoner.

931
00:46:36,445 --> 00:46:38,099
- There's my baby.

932
00:46:38,143 --> 00:46:39,492
I'm gonna marry him.

933
00:46:39,535 --> 00:46:40,710
[laughs]

934
00:46:40,754 --> 00:46:43,670
He could put his shoes
under my bed any time.

935
00:46:43,713 --> 00:46:45,411
- Aunt Lily.

936
00:46:45,454 --> 00:46:47,892
- [Man On TV] Scott was court
martialed, found guilty,

937
00:46:47,935 --> 00:46:50,590
and sentenced to 30
years at hard labor.

938
00:46:50,633 --> 00:46:53,680
It happened the night
of April 20th, 1983.

939
00:46:53,723 --> 00:46:57,031
- [Lindsey On TV] In a situation
like this, nobody wins.

940
00:46:57,075 --> 00:47:01,166
The victim doesn't win, I
don't win being innocent.

941
00:47:01,209 --> 00:47:04,082
I just hope everything
straightens itself out.

942
00:47:04,125 --> 00:47:05,648
- [Man On TV] The military
revue board has ruled

943
00:47:05,692 --> 00:47:07,955
that Scott is entitled
to a Dubay hearing.

944
00:47:07,999 --> 00:47:10,218
Not a new trial, but
a hearing to decide

945
00:47:10,262 --> 00:47:12,742
whether he received
a proper defense.

946
00:47:12,786 --> 00:47:14,657
- I guess they didn't
need my interview.

947
00:47:14,701 --> 00:47:16,355
- [Man On TV] He
may get a new trial.

948
00:47:16,398 --> 00:47:19,358
The Marine Corps has
declined to comment.

949
00:47:19,401 --> 00:47:20,881
- Millions of people
now are gonna know about

950
00:47:20,925 --> 00:47:23,057
the Lindsey Scott case.

951
00:47:23,101 --> 00:47:24,885
- That's right, honey.

952
00:47:31,457 --> 00:47:32,197
- Hmm.

953
00:47:39,378 --> 00:47:40,248
Oh, honey.

954
00:47:40,292 --> 00:47:43,469
I feel like such a proud fool.

955
00:47:43,512 --> 00:47:46,341
Inviting everybody over
here seeing me on TV

956
00:47:46,385 --> 00:47:49,431
like I'm Betty
Davis or something.

957
00:47:49,475 --> 00:47:54,436
- Honey, this is an incredible
thing and you made it happen.

958
00:47:54,480 --> 00:47:56,047
So, congratulations.

959
00:47:58,440 --> 00:47:59,877
- Thanks, honey.

960
00:48:01,487 --> 00:48:02,270
Oh, well.

961
00:48:03,619 --> 00:48:05,404
That was my big debut.

962
00:48:06,622 --> 00:48:10,017
[slow trumpet music]

963
00:48:10,061 --> 00:48:11,801
- [Crowd] Free Lindsey Scott.

964
00:48:11,845 --> 00:48:13,673
Free Lindsey Scott.

965
00:48:13,716 --> 00:48:14,979
Free Lindsey Scott.

966
00:48:15,022 --> 00:48:17,546
- Wow, all this for
a Dubay hearing.

967
00:48:17,590 --> 00:48:20,332
- It's the power of 60 Minutes.

968
00:48:27,861 --> 00:48:31,952
- After April 22, did you next
have a meeting of substance

969
00:48:31,996 --> 00:48:35,129
with Mr. Kuhnke where
presentation of evidence

970
00:48:35,173 --> 00:48:39,090
or exploration of
defenses was discussed?

