00:48:43,877 --> 00:48:45,618
- Never again, sir.

974
00:48:46,532 --> 00:48:49,796
- Could you elaborate
on this, Private?

975
00:48:49,839 --> 00:48:51,189
- Well, sir.

976
00:48:51,232 --> 00:48:55,323
I asked Mr. Kuhnke by
telephone several times

977
00:48:55,367 --> 00:48:57,238
to bring in the witnesses.

978
00:48:57,282 --> 00:49:01,329
Mr. Kuhnke repeatedly told
me not to worry about it

979
00:49:01,373 --> 00:49:05,594
'cause he didn't think the
case would go to trial.

980
00:49:08,641 --> 00:49:11,383
- Private Scott,
in your estimation,

981
00:49:11,426 --> 00:49:14,125
did you have 20 visits
to Mr. Kuhnke's office?

982
00:49:14,168 --> 00:49:15,561
- No.

983
00:49:15,604 --> 00:49:19,565
- Did you have 10
visits to his office?

984
00:49:19,608 --> 00:49:20,392
- No.

985
00:49:22,263 --> 00:49:25,005
- Well, how many visits did
you have alone with Mr. Kuhnke

986
00:49:25,049 --> 00:49:29,227
where you maintained
your innocence and
discussed your case?

987
00:49:30,576 --> 00:49:31,359
- One.

988
00:49:32,534 --> 00:49:36,277
- And that's your
testimony under oath?

989
00:49:36,321 --> 00:49:37,452
- Yes, it is.

990
00:49:41,413 --> 00:49:43,763
- Mr. Kuhnke, in going
to trial you stated

991
00:49:43,806 --> 00:49:45,634
you didn't prep any
of the witnesses?

992
00:49:45,678 --> 00:49:46,984
- That's right.

993
00:49:48,028 --> 00:49:49,073
I had talked.

994
00:49:50,074 --> 00:49:50,813
I had...

995
00:49:50,857 --> 00:49:52,032
- Wait, wait.

