997
00:49:55,470 --> 00:49:59,431
- Attempted murder, rape,
sodomy, forceful abduction.

998
00:50:00,693 --> 00:50:02,390
- And you didn't prep
any of the witnesses?

999
00:50:02,434 --> 00:50:05,480
- I didn't prep them, no.

1000
00:50:05,524 --> 00:50:07,787
- Did you prep Private Scott?

1001
00:50:09,571 --> 00:50:10,616
- I didn't have to.

1002
00:50:10,659 --> 00:50:11,443
- Why not?

1003
00:50:13,445 --> 00:50:15,882
- He professed his innocence

1004
00:50:17,275 --> 00:50:20,017
and I told him to
tell the truth.

1005
00:50:21,888 --> 00:50:22,671
- Okay.

1006
00:50:23,933 --> 00:50:24,717
All right.

1007
00:50:25,848 --> 00:50:28,416
Let me think, let me think.

1008
00:50:28,460 --> 00:50:32,377
Okay, on April 20th I
arrested both these guys

1009
00:50:32,420 --> 00:50:34,074
for shoplifting.

1010
00:50:34,118 --> 00:50:35,380
And I made a note

1011
00:50:39,775 --> 00:50:42,517
about a third guy who I thought

1012
00:50:43,866 --> 00:50:45,781
was a part of the team.

1013
00:50:48,523 --> 00:50:50,177
Oh, see.

1014
00:50:50,221 --> 00:50:51,091
Here it is.

1015
00:50:52,440 --> 00:50:54,007
This note, this guy.

1016
00:50:54,051 --> 00:50:55,965
This is Lindsey Scott.

1017
00:50:56,009 --> 00:50:57,402
I am sure of it.

1018
00:50:58,577 --> 00:50:59,621
- You'll testify to that?

1019
00:50:59,665 --> 00:51:01,188
- Are you kidding
will I testify?

1020
00:51:01,232 --> 00:51:03,321
You bet I will testify.

1021
00:51:03,364 --> 00:51:05,801
- And it is now your
testimony, under oath,

1022
00:51:05,845 --> 00:51:08,804
that on the night
of April 20th, 1983,

1023
00:51:08,848 --> 00:51:11,633
between the hours of
eight and 8:30 p.m.,

1024
00:51:11,677 --> 00:51:16,247
one Lindsey Scott was present
at a Zayre's Department Store?

1025
00:51:16,290 --> 00:51:17,596
- That's correct.

1026
00:51:19,032 --> 00:51:20,468
- Thank you, Ms. Hills.

1027
00:51:20,512 --> 00:51:22,122
You may step down.

1028
00:51:22,166 --> 00:51:25,169
[people chattering]

1029
00:51:38,747 --> 00:51:41,359
Your Honor, the
defense rests its case

1030
00:51:41,402 --> 00:51:43,317
and moves for a
dismissal of all charges

1031
00:51:43,361 --> 00:51:45,363
against Lindsey Scott.

1032
00:51:45,406 --> 00:51:48,409
- We'll take a recess
while I make my decision.

1033
00:51:48,453 --> 00:51:50,281
[gavel bangs]

1034
00:51:50,324 --> 00:51:52,718
[tense music]

1035
00:52:16,524 --> 00:52:19,527
The defense motion for a
dismissal of the charges

1036
00:52:19,571 --> 00:52:22,487
against Private Scott is denied.

1037
00:52:22,530 --> 00:52:23,836
I have no authority beyond that

1038
00:52:23,879 --> 00:52:25,533
which is given me in the order.

1039
00:52:25,577 --> 00:52:28,493
However, given the
facts of this case,

1040
00:52:28,536 --> 00:52:30,756
I am recommending
that this be referred

1041
00:52:30,799 --> 00:52:33,062
to General Tumi for review.

