00:52:35,674 --> 00:52:38,111
- Your Honor, we feel
that freeing Private Scott

1043
00:52:38,155 --> 00:52:40,461
to his family with
appropriate restrictions

1044
00:52:40,505 --> 00:52:42,333
is in the interest of justice.

1045
00:52:42,376 --> 00:52:43,551
- I'm sorry, Counselor.

1046
00:52:43,595 --> 00:52:46,337
I have no authority to
grant such a request.

1047
00:52:46,380 --> 00:52:48,469
It'll have to be
up to General Tumi.

