1146
00:59:14,507 --> 00:59:17,554
I want to try and boost
your immune system.

1147
00:59:17,597 --> 00:59:20,687
The important thing
now is to get rest

1148
00:59:20,731 --> 00:59:23,864
and to conserve your energy.

1149
00:59:23,908 --> 00:59:27,651
- Doc, could you just give
