1150
00:59:27,694 --> 00:59:28,608
- Yeah.

1151
00:59:28,652 --> 00:59:30,349
- Yeah, just a minute alone.

1152
00:59:30,392 --> 00:59:31,350
That's all.

1153
00:59:31,393 --> 00:59:32,133
- [Doctor] I'll just be...

1154
00:59:32,177 --> 00:59:32,960
- Thanks.

1155
00:59:44,624 --> 00:59:45,407
Honey.

1156
00:59:48,106 --> 00:59:50,587
- Don't look at me like that.

1157
01:00:04,644 --> 01:00:06,994
