01:07:49,413 --> 01:07:50,283
- Yeah, thanks.

1291
01:07:50,327 --> 01:07:51,589
- I hope it's not too strong.

1292
01:07:51,632 --> 01:07:53,243
This stuff will make
you stand up for sure.

1293
01:07:53,286 --> 01:07:55,984
[Myers laughs]

1294
01:07:56,028 --> 01:07:58,335
[coughing]

1295
01:08:01,425 --> 01:08:03,427
[door slams]

1296
01:08:03,470 --> 01:08:06,473
Hey, I was wondering
where you were.

1297
01:08:08,562 --> 01:08:10,608
- I went to the hospital.

1298
01:08:10,651 --> 01:08:12,392
- What happened, baby?

1299
01:08:12,436 --> 01:08:13,828
- I had a talk with your doctor.

1300
01:08:13,872 --> 01:08:17,963
He said I needed to have
a conversation with you.

1301
01:08:21,488 --> 01:08:23,534
- I think we should have
this conversation...

1302
01:08:23,577 --> 01:08:24,926
Sweetheart, we have company.

1303
01:08:24,970 --> 01:08:25,710
We should just go in...

1304
01:08:25,753 --> 01:08:27,581
- I don't wan to go.

1305
01:08:29,714 --> 01:08:31,846
Exactly how sick are you?

1306
01:08:35,285 --> 01:08:36,460
- I'm very sick.

1307
01:08:38,157 --> 01:08:39,071
- How sick?

1308
01:08:51,736 --> 01:08:53,129
- I have cancer.

1309
01:09:00,527 --> 01:09:03,051
- What are they doing about it?

1310
01:09:04,444 --> 01:09:07,534
- There's nothing
they can do about it.

1311
01:09:09,145 --> 01:09:11,451
- Why didn't you tell me?

1312
